oin the unrivaled reality and military engagement. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> More contents will be coming. </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882910/extras/2c535d0ce0861bf66ed8a2906810c4a5.poster.avif?t=1543990792\" width=680 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882910/extras/2c535d0ce0861bf66ed8a2906810c4a5.webm?t=1543990792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882910/extras/2c535d0ce0861bf66ed8a2906810c4a5.mp4?t=1543990792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
